{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/Comp_23.gif?t=1727200339\" /><br><br><strong>ROGUELIKE DECKBUILDER MEETS GRID-BASED COMBAT</strong><br><br>\u2013 Craft a deck of synergized abilities, moves, and skills<br>\u2013 Slide around enemies, perform combos, and use the environment to your advantage<br>\u2013 Adapt your playstyle with card upgrades, game-changing infusions, and agent patches<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/Comp_24.gif?t=1727200339\" /><br><br><strong>ORIGINAL SYNTHWAVE SOUNDTRACK</strong><br><br>30+ new tracks from the talents of the Synthwave and Darksynth genres.<br>Composed exclusively for Nitro Kid by:<br>- LudoWic (Katana Zero OST)<br>- Tonebox<br>- Jules Reves<br>- Laird Kruger<br><br>OST is available for purchase separately or in the Turbo Bundle with Nitro Kid.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/cassette2.gif?t=1727200339\" /><br><br><strong>RETROFUTURE ESSENCE</strong><br> <br>It has everything we love about the 80\u2019s with cyberpunk, retrowave, and classic action movie references. Can you catch all the easter eggs we hid?<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/agents3.png?t=1727200339\" /><br><strong>THREE UNIQUE AGENTS</strong><br><br>Pick your special agent. Every one of them has a unique set of cards, abilities, and playstyles.<br><br><strong>L33</strong> \u2014 Fluid fighter dedicated to martial arts and the power of the elements. <br>When Kung fu isn\u2019t enough, you ignite in fury, burning enemies down (<i>quite literally</i>).<br><br><strong>J4X</strong> \u2014 Heavy-hitter thinking like a chess player. <br>Tank with the unique ability to counter-attack during enemy turns. Build up Combo and Pressure points for devastating knock-outs!<br><br><strong>K31</strong> \u2014 Professional assassin, the best at tech and weaponry.<br>Possessing two different stances for ranged and close combat. Each stance comes with unique perks and limitations. Use your ammo wisely!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/Three_Agents.gif?t=1727200339\" /><br><br><strong>10 SECURITY LEVELS FOR A REAL CHALLENGE</strong><br><br>Every time you clear INFINITY tower \u2013 a new Security Level is unlocked.<br>Each of them brings tougher challenges your way. Will you make it to the mysterious <i>Creator</i>?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/Floors_2.gif?t=1727200339\" /><br><br><strong>NITRO KID FEATURES</strong><br><br>- 3 unlockable Agents<br>- 250+ Cards<br>- 3 unique Acts (stages of INFINITY tower)<br>- Security Levels for difficulty progression<br>- 50+ Unique Enemies<br>- 50+ Events<br>- 30+ Infusions<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709050/extras/Events.gif?t=1727200339\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Mitts On","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709050/343b7ff0599e8b27afcf1155a1ac9d6845e8bdca.jpg"},{"name":"Mission Complete","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709050/7adfc9fbbc70609c3a209be668a828fa88beef78.jpg"},{"name":"Target Practice","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709050/a9b382217c2f33ddbfca8fba7df53c62f238e58c.jpg"},{"name":"Rogue Runner","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709050/dbc61845b8272fc85101a000a856e1d6a9beadfb.jpg"},{"name":"Decked Out","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1709050/52c277c4af1e663ffa7e7264f5c334392